msgid "Creating a New User Profile"
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:5
msgid "Open the Program"
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:7
msgid ""
"Tap the **BTT Recorder icon** on the tablet screen. This icon may not be "
"on the main screen; you may need to scroll to a different screen to find "
"it, or open your apps. You can then tap and drag it to the main screen if"
" desired."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:9
msgid ""
"The first time you open the program, tap **ALLOW** to grant BTT Recorder "
"access to media files, and then tap **ALLOW** to give the program "
"permission to record audio."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:12
msgid "Create a New User Profile"
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:14
msgid "To create a new User profile, tap the **New User** card."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:16
msgid "New User Card"
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:22
msgid "Read, or have someone read to you, the three Terms of Use."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:24
msgid "Tap on each of the green bars."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:25
msgid ""
"Read the content. You may need to scroll to see the entire contents of "
"the ‘Translation Guidelines’."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:26
msgid "Tap on ‘Close’ at the bottom of each of the windows."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:28
msgid "**Note**: Tapping on the green 'NO THANKS' link closes the program."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:30
msgid ""
"Tap the green I AGREE link at the bottom of the window if you agree with "
"all three statements."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:32
msgid "Tap the Record icon (microphone) and record your name or pseudonym."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:34
msgid ""
"A pseudonym is a false name that is used instead of the real name of the "
"person doing the work. You could use a pseudonym if you are concerned "
"that being associated with Bible translation work would compromise your "
"safety or that of your family."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:36
msgid ""
"You will need to record your name while the red circle is going around – "
"3 seconds."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:38
msgid "Press the play button to listen to the recording."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:40
msgid ""
"If you can you hear your voice and understand your words, then tap the "
"green Yes button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:42
msgid "Accept Recording of Name"
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:48
msgid ""
"If your voice is too soft or you cannot understand your words, then tap "
"the Redo button to make another recording."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:50
msgid "Redo Recording of Name"
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:56
msgid ""
"When you accept the recording - the opening recording screen opens, and "
"you are ready to start a new project."
msgstr ""

#: ../../createuser.rst:58
msgid ""
"**NOTE**: If you want to create another user, you can log out of the "
"program (see `The 3-dot (Options) Menu <https://btt-"
"recorder.readthedocs.io/en/latest/menus.html#the-3-dot-menu-on-the-"
"project-management-screen-home-screen>`_)"
msgstr ""

